title: Blocks From the Lake, $50 Monthly Move In Special, Video Walkthrough
posting_body: ['2nd Floor, Blocks from Bde Maka Ska, , Heat Paid, $50 Monthly Move In Special', 'Property Address', '3554 Emerson Ave S. - #10 | Minneapolis, MN 55408', 'Available: 07/29/2022', 'Offered By', 'Guardian Property Management |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'In person showings available.', 'This unit is ready for move in anytime before Aug 15th.', 'Video walkthrough and pictures of the unit are available on the Guardian Property Management website.', '$50 off per month for the 1st lease term with any lease longer than 12 month.', 'Located just south of uptown blocks from the lake this apartment is close to everything including transportation.', 'Laundry is available in the building (Coin Operated)', 'Bedroom 9x11 with closet.', 'Air Conditioner unit.', 'As a tenant you are only responsible for electric.', 'Street Parking Only.', 'Pets are welcome with positive rental reference and credit.', '(Dog fee $30mo, Cat fee $20mo)', 'Applications are available on the Guardian Property Management website.', 'Each application is $50 per adult and can be paid with a credit or debit card.', 'Application is based on income, credit history (Guardian Property Management will not use credit score but will be using information from your credit report), rental/work history and includes a criminal background check.', 'For full criteria visit our website and click “apply now” on the listed unit.', 'Any additional questions please call or email Billy.', 'Broker: GUARDIAN PROPERTY MANAGEMENT AND SERVICES LLC', 'Agent:', 'Billy Sommers', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 500', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $950.00', 'Available: 07/29/2022', 'Application Fee: $50.00', 'Security Deposit: $950.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs allowed']
